@LoanApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5131

### Get all loans
GET {{LoanApi_HostAddress}}/api/loans
Accept: application/json

###

### Get specific loan
GET {{LoanApi_HostAddress}}/api/loans/LN-001
Accept: application/json

###

### Create new loan
POST {{LoanApi_HostAddress}}/api/loans
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "loanNumber": "LN-001",
  "clientName": "John Doe",
  "amount": 50000,
  "requestDate": "2025-12-16T10:00:00",
  "status": "Pending"
}

###

### Update loan
PUT {{LoanApi_HostAddress}}/api/loans/LN-001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "loanNumber": "LN-001",
  "clientName": "John Doe",
  "amount": 55000,
  "requestDate": "2025-12-16T10:00:00",
  "status": "Approved"
}

###

### Delete loan
DELETE {{LoanApi_HostAddress}}/api/loans/LN-001

###
